This is an excellent comfort food recipe! Easy and quick. I like the fact that the cheese is added to the bread crumbs, rather than mixed in with the noodles. For my casserole, I used some leftover french bread that I had toasted with olive oil, garlic and herbes de provence, and it added a wonderful dimension. Will definitely make again!

