Satisfying comfort food that doesn't come from a box?! Sign me up!!! Don't be daunted by the three pan and a casserole dish issue. This recipe with a little planning can be done in a little amount of time Think about making the roux in the same pan you sauteed the mushrooms in - now you're using two pots and a casserole dish. Bump up the milk with half and half to taste - 30 minutes for a great dish. I'll make this again and again.

