Rating: 3
this is great comfort food, much better than what I grew up on, only thing... dirtys up alot of dishes.

Rating: 3
If you want fast stick to the can of mushroom soup. But you can speed this recipe up by multitasking. I started the water and the onions at the same time. While the onions were sautéing I sliced the mushrooms. When I added the mushrooms to the onions I started the roux. The mushrooms and noodles were done before the béchamel, so I did the topping and drained the tuna. When the sauce was done I mixed it all together. I also agree with the extra can of tuna and added some white pepper, garlic powder, and celery salt.

Rating: 3
